<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8">
		<meta http-equiv="content-type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
		<meta name="description" content="" />
		<meta name="keywords" content="" />
		<!--[if lte IE 8]><script src="js/html5shiv.js"></script><![endif]-->

    <script src="js/jquery.min.js"></script>
		<script src="js/skel.min.js"></script>
		<script src="js/skel-layers.min.js"></script>
		<script src="js/init.js"></script>
		<noscript>
      <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/font-awesome.css" />
			<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/skel.css" />
			<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css.erb" />
			<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style-xlarge.css" />
		</noscript>

	</head>
	<body class="landing">

		<!-- Header -->

      <header id="header">
				<h1>Welcome</h1>
				<nav id="nav">
					<ul>
						<li><%=link_to 'Home', '/' %></li>

						<li><%=link_to 'Already have an account?', 'login', class: "button special" %></li>
					</ul>
				</nav>
			</header>


		<!-- Banner -->
			<section id="banner">
				<h2>QMi</h2>
				<p>In a world so busy, it's no wonder why people need effective
        solutions to meeting new and interesting people. You came to the
        right place.
        </p>

        <p class="lead">
          <%= link_to "Sign me up!", 'signup', class: "button" %>
        </p>
			</section>

    <!--First Section -->
    <!-- One -->
			<section id="one" class="wrapper style1 special">
				<div class="container">
					<header class="major">
						<h2>It's never been easier.</h2>
						<p>What are some of the features I can expect?</p>
					</header>
					<div class="row 150%">
						<div class="4u 12u$(medium)">
							<section class="box">
								<i class="icon big rounded color1 fa fa-cog fa-3x"></i>
								<h3>Fill Out a Questionnaire</h3>
								<p>Create a series of questions using our integrated tools which other
                users will have to answer. When they're done, their answers will be sent to
              you and if you like what their responses were, accept it and you can begin
            chatting immediately!</p>
							</section>
						</div>
						<div class="4u 12u$(medium)">
							<section class="box">
								<i class="icon big rounded color9 fa-wrench fa-3x"></i>
								<h3>Set Your Preferences</h3>
								<p>Choose from a variety of matchmaking preferences, such as geographical radius,
                  or gender -- and we'll take care of the rest.
                the rest.</p>
							</section>
						</div>
						<div class="4u$ 12u$(medium)">
							<section class="box">
								<i class="icon big rounded color6 fa-heart fa-3x"></i>
								<h3>Match With Compatible People</h3>
								<p>On top of having a short profile bibliography, we'll help you create a more
                authentic experience with other people through our unique questionnaire system --
              ensuring you don't get weirdos or people that don't have the same mindset as you.</p>
							</section>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

      <!-- end -->

      <!-- Second Section -->
      <section id="two" class="wrapper style2 special">
				<div class="container">
					<header class="major">
						<h2>Don't believe us?</h2>
						<p>Check out some testimonials from REAL users.</p>
					</header>
					<section class="profiles">
						<div class="row">
							<section class="3u 6u(medium) 12u$(xsmall) profile">
							 <%= image_tag('profile_placeholder.gif') %>
								<h4>Michael Jones</h4>
								<p>I was on Tinder before I found QMi, and it was the greatest
                switch I've ever made. I've met authentic people who have more in common
              with me, and it's amazing.</p>
							</section>
							<section class="3u 6u$(medium) 12u$(xsmall) profile">
								<%= image_tag('profile_placeholder.gif') %>
								<h4>Sharon Smith</h4>
								<p>All other online dating apps I've tried have left me feeling
                unsatisified and like I've wasted my time. QMi is great.</p>
							</section>
							<section class="3u 6u(medium) 12u$(xsmall) profile">
								<%= image_tag('profile_placeholder.gif') %>
								<h4>Bobby Chan</h4>
								<p>QMi is a great application for anyone who's serious about
                the online dating scene. It's never been easier to get meet
              like-minded individuals who share a similar mindset to yours.</p>
							</section>
							<section class="3u$ 6u$(medium) 12u$(xsmall) profile">
								<%= image_tag('profile_placeholder.gif') %>
								<h4>Karen Vesuvius</h4>
								<p>I love it. Simply put.</p>
							</section>
						</div>
					</section>


	</body>
</html>
